# CQ-C8: What confidence score is associated with a moral-value annotation?
PREFIX amor: <http://www.gsi.upm.es/ontologies/amor/ns#>
PREFIX itsrdf: <http://www.w3.org/2005/11/its/rdf#>

SELECT ?annotation ?confidence
WHERE {
  ?annotation a amor:MoralValueAnnotation ;
    itsrdf:taConfidence ?confidence .
}
ORDER BY ?annotation ?confidence
